channel.title: 8-bit Produk Style Challenge (CLOSED)
channel.description:
New challenge from Osharu Perez! Make a song in the style of Produk, BUT, the sounds you use **HAVE** to make the song sound like an 8-bit track. If you don't know what an 8-bit track sound like, think NES, or SNES. **ONLY RESPOND IF YOU ARE ENTERING THIS CONTEST!!** The winner shall be announced as the new Produk (just kidding), and shall be announced May 14th!
[details="Summary"] Make a song in the style of Produk, but it has to sound 8-bit. **ONLY REPLY IF YOU ARE ENTERING THE CONTEST! PLEASE AND THANK YOU!** [/details]
**Entries Deadline:** May 11th **Winner Announcement:** May 14th
